text: Jessica Lokhorst (born 16 August 1993) is a Dutch korfball player. She is a member of Fortuna and the Netherlands national korfball team. She missed the 2021 European championships, due to an ankle injury. With the national team she became champion at the 2022 World Games in Birmingham, Alabama. ==Achievements== ===Club=== *Korfball Europa Cup champion, 1x (2020) * champion, 2x (2019, 2022) *Goal of the year award, 1x (2020) ===National team=== *World Games champion, 2x (2022) *World champion, 1x (2019) *European champion, 1x (2018) ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch korfball players Category:Sportspeople from Gelderland Category:Sportswomen
